### Upstream attribution

Source data derived from:
- 殆知阁古代文献 (https://github.com/garychowcmu/daizhigev20) — 1.7B-character corpus
  of classical Chinese texts assembled by 殆知阁
- chinese-poetry (https://github.com/chinese-poetry/chinese-poetry) — 诗经/四书 JSONs

Both upstream sources are themselves derived from public-domain texts.
